author: Xbox
description:
A new chapter awaits. Prepare for the third thrilling chapter of Braking Point in F1® 25, out May 30. Play 3 days early with the Iconic Edition: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/f1-25-iconic-edition/9MW14RS3PRJN/0017

The legacy of the Konnersport team is at stake as a dramatic event throws the team into chaos. Can the team fight back and finally put itself in contention for the World Championship?

This thrilling chapter introduces new features that let you experience the story your way, including alternative scenarios where you choose which driver to play in key races. Your choices lead to different on-track objectives, and even a different take on the story’s exciting conclusion.

#F125 #EAF1 #EASPORTSF1
